.SS Bumping Build Number
\f[CR]agvtool bump \-all\f[R] increments the build number, which
increments both:
.IP "1." 3
The \(lqBuild\(rq field in Xcode\(cqs Target General Settings, which is
the \f[CR]CFBundleVersion\f[R] in the \f[CR]Info.plist\f[R]
.IP "2." 3
The \(lqCurrent Project Version\(rq, in Xcode\(cqs Project \(lqBuild
Settings\(rq under \(lqVersioning\(rq, which is the
\f[CR]CURRENT_PROJECT_VERSION\f[R] in the \f[CR]project.pbxproj\f[R]
file.
.PP
This is why those two numbers much have the same value.
